| ---------- | ---------- | -------- |
| `fig_r_prog_by_tier` | `fig28_r_prog_by_tier` | 28 |
| `fig_cfp_by_tier` | `fig29_cfp_by_tier` | 29 |
| `fig_pr_revert_by_tier` | `fig30_pr_revert_by_tier` | 30 |

Confirmed: fig27 (`fig27_impl_rate_distribution`) was the previous ceiling.

